  <brief_title>Study to Evaluate the Effect of SLV320 in Addition to Chronic Furosemide Treatment on Renal Function in Subjects With Congestive Heart Failure and Impaired Renal Function</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled, Multi-Center, Sequential Cohort Study to Evaluate the Effect of SLV320 in Addition to Chronic Furosemide Treatment on Renal Function in Subjects With Congestive Heart Failure and Impaired Renal Function</official_title>
